videos.headline: Ole Miss steamrolls Gonzaga to open NCAA play
videos.description: The 8-seed Rebels shut down the 9-seed Bulldogs with tenacious defense, holding them to 1-of-16 shooting on 3-pointers (.063) in a dominating 71-48 NCAA tourney win.
